public abstract class AbstractPercentilesAggregationBuilder<T extends AbstractPercentilesAggregationBuilder<T>>
extends ValuesSourceAggregationBuilder.LeafOnly<ValuesSource,​T>
This provides a base class for aggregations that are building percentiles or percentiles-like functionality (e.g. percentile ranks). It provides a set of common fields/functionality for setting the available algorithms (TDigest and HDRHistogram), as well as algorithm-specific settings via a PercentilesConfig object
